.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
City: paris, hamburg, edinburgh, berlin, rome, hannover, prague
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to hannover and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the italian##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
8. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| City          | rome | edinburgh | hannover | hamburg | prague | paris      | berlin  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

