.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, german, indian, mexican, pakistani, polish
House: victorian, cape-cod, wooden, ranch-style, farmhouse, townhouse, cottage
 1. the mexican is on the left of the canadian##1
 2. the wooden house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 3. the farmhouse house is the polish##1
 4. the german is on the left of the pakistani##1
 5. the victorian house is on the left of the cottage house##1
 6. the indian is the ranch-style house##1
 7. the canadian is on the left of the wooden house##1
 8. the victorian house is between the cottage house and the indian##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the townhouse house##1
10. the dutch is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | canadian | dutch   | indian | german | pakistani |
| House           | farmhouse | townhouse     | cape-cod     | wooden | ranch-style   | victorian   | cottage    |

