.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
There 7 different types of food: tomato, cucumber, cranberry, garlic, cherry, plum, lemon
 1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
 3. the person eating plum is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 5. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking water##2
 7. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 8. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking water and the person drinking cola##2
11. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | lemonade   | cola         | fanta     | water              | mirinda    | juice     |
| Food        | plum | cucumber | cherry | garlic | lemon | tomato | cranberry |

