.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, soy-milk, milk, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, lemonade
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, sailing, skateboarding, tennis, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person drinking milk is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person drinking cola##2
7. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking lemonade##2
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Beverage   | lemonade | almond-milk       | soy-milk    | hot-chocolate | milk | cola     | fanta       |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | skateboarding | volleyball | tennis        | sailing | ice-hockey | weightlifting |

