.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-16::.
7 different pets are kept: dog, rabbit, pony, hedgehog, ferret, hamster, snake
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, climbing, golf, handball, parkour, surfing
1. the owner of the pony is between the person who's sport is climbing and the owner of the dog##2
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the snake and the person who's sport is parkour##2
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
9. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |     3     |     4     |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Pet   | hamster  | ferret | snake    | hedgehog | dog | pony  | rabbit  |
| Sport   | handball | surfing       | badminton | golf      | parkour     | baseball | climbing |

